Variable.name: id
Description: Participant ID number.

Variable.name: day
Description: Day of week (1 = Sunday, …, 7 = Saturday).

Variable.name: valid_day
Description: 1 if day is considered valid for analysis, otherwise 0.

Variable.name: valid_days
Description: Number of valid days (only included in per-person summary).

Variable.name: valid_week_days
Description: Number of valid weekdays (only included in per-person summary).

Variable.name: valid_weekend_days
Description: Number of valid weekend days (only included in per-person summary).

Variable.name: include
Description: 1 if participant is considered to have valid data for analysis, otherwise 0.

Variable.name: valid_min
Description: Number of minutes classified as valid wear time.

Variable.name: counts
Description: Total counts accumulated during wear time minutes.

Variable.name: cpm
Description: counts/valid_min.

Variable.name: steps
Description: Total steps accumulated during weartime minutes.

Variable.name: sed_min
Description: Sedentary minutes, or minutes with counts < int_cuts[1].

Variable.name: light_min
Description: Light intensity minutes (int.cuts[1] <= counts < int.cuts[2]).

Variable.name: life_min
Description: Lifestyle intensity minutes (int.cuts[2] <= counts < int.cuts[3]).

Variable.name: mod_min
Description: Moderate intensity minutes (int.cuts[3] <= counts < int.cuts[4]).

Variable.name: vig_min
Description: Vigorous intensity minutes (counts >= int.cuts[4]).

Variable.name: lightlife_min
Description: Light-to-lifestyle intensity minutes (int.cuts[1] <= counts < int.cuts[3]).

Variable.name: mvpa_min
Description: Moderate-to-vigorous intensity minutes (counts >= int.cuts[3]).

Variable.name: active_min
Description: Active (i.e. non-sedentary) minutes (counts >= int.cuts[1]).

Variable.name: sed_percent
Description: sed_min/valid_min.

Variable.name: light_percent
Description: light_min/valid_min.

Variable.name: life_percent
Description: life_min/valid_min.

Variable.name: mod_percent
Description: mod_min/valid_min.

Variable.name: vig_percent
Description: vig_min/valid_min.

Variable.name: lightlife_percent
Description: lightlife_min/valid_min.

Variable.name: mvpa_percent
Description: mvpa_min/valid_min.

Variable.name: active_percent
Description: active_min/valid_min.

Variable.name: sed_counts
Description: Counts from sedentary time.

Variable.name: light_counts
Description: Counts from light activity.

Variable.name: life_counts
Description: Counts from lifestyle activity.

Variable.name: mod_counts
Description: Counts from moderate activity.

Variable.name: vig_counts
Description: Counts from vigorous activity.

Variable.name: lightlife_counts
Description: Counts from light-to-lifestyle activity.

Variable.name: mvpa_counts
Description: Counts from MVPA.

Variable.name: active_counts
Description: Counts from active (i.e. non-sedentary) time.

Variable.name: sed_bouted_10min
Description: Sedentary minutes accumulated in bouts of length >= 10 min.

Variable.name: sed_bouted_30min
Description: Sedentary minutes accumulated in bouts of length >= 30 min.

Variable.name: sed_bouted_60min
Description: Sedentary minutes accumulated in bouts of length >= 60 min.

Variable.name: sed_breaks
Description: Number of times that participant transitions from sedentary minute to non-sedentary minute.

Variable.name: max_1min_counts
Description: Maximum count value.

Variable.name: max_5min_counts
Description: Maximum average count value over a 5-min interval.

Variable.name: max_10min_counts
Description: Maximum average count value over a 10-min interval.

Variable.name: max_30min_counts
Description: Maximum average count value over a 30-min interval.

Variable.name: num_mvpa_bouts
Description: Number of MVPA bouts per day.

Variable.name: num_vig_bouts
Description: Number of vigorous bouts per day.

Variable.name: mvpa_bouted
Description: MVPA minutes accumulated in bouts of length >= active.bout.length (by default 10-min bouts).

Variable.name: vig_bouted
Description: Vigorous intensity minutes accumulated in bouts of length >= active.bout.length (by default 10-min bouts).

Variable.name: guideline_min
Description: Minutes towards physical activity guidelines (150 min/wk of MVPA or 75 min/wk of vigorous physical activity).

Variable.name: cpm_hour1
Description: Average counts per minute during hour 1 (midnight to 1 AM).

Variable.name: cpm_hour2
Description: Average counts per minute during hour 2.

Variable.name: cpm_hour3
Description: Average counts per minute during hour 3.

Variable.name: cpm_hour4
Description: Average counts per minute during hour 4.

Variable.name: cpm_hour5
Description: Average counts per minute during hour 5.

Variable.name: cpm_hour6
Description: Average counts per minute during hour 6.

Variable.name: cpm_hour7
Description: Average counts per minute during hour 7.

Variable.name: cpm_hour8
Description: Average counts per minute during hour 8.

Variable.name: cpm_hour9
Description: Average counts per minute during hour 9.

Variable.name: cpm_hour10
Description: Average counts per minute during hour 10.

Variable.name: cpm_hour11
Description: Average counts per minute during hour 11.

Variable.name: cpm_hour12
Description: Average counts per minute during hour 12.

Variable.name: cpm_hour13
Description: Average counts per minute during hour 13.

Variable.name: cpm_hour14
Description: Average counts per minute during hour 14.

Variable.name: cpm_hour15
Description: Average counts per minute during hour 15.

Variable.name: cpm_hour16
Description: Average counts per minute during hour 16.

Variable.name: cpm_hour17
Description: Average counts per minute during hour 17.

Variable.name: cpm_hour18
Description: Average counts per minute during hour 18.

Variable.name: cpm_hour19
Description: Average counts per minute during hour 19.

Variable.name: cpm_hour20
Description: Average counts per minute during hour 20.

Variable.name: cpm_hour21
Description: Average counts per minute during hour 21.

Variable.name: cpm_hour22
Description: Average counts per minute during hour 22.

Variable.name: cpm_hour23
Description: Average counts per minute during hour 23.

Variable.name: cpm_hour24
Description: Average counts per minute during hour 24 (11 PM to midnight).
